channel.title: Generic RS2 Loader (Version 1 RC)
channel.description:
Generic RS2Loader | Version 1 RC | By Joseph Melsha
[b]Version 2 coming in around 3 hours![/b]
RS2Loader loads the RS2 loader softly to avoid detection and allows you to play RuneScape remotely from Jagex's website.
Features:
[ul][li]You can enable HD gameplay[/li] [li]You have a 0.003% chance of getting banned[/li][/ul]
Updates:
[ul][li]Added a GNU GPL license[/li] [li]Fixed the remaining noticeable bugs.[/li][/ul]
org.sirox.rs2loader.loader is very disorganized, I pushed different parts into this quickly.
Files included: readme.txt license.txt run.bat make.bat bin/ src/org/sirox/rs2loader/*.java
All info about this program is located in readme.txt in the file:
Give me feedback and report error's to me on this topic board!
Mirror(s): [url=http://uppit.com/v/3WHADF8B]http://uppit.com/v/3WHADF8B[/url]
